<hgroup><h1>Use of Recalled Devices in New Device Authorizations Under the US Food and Drug Administration’s 510(k) Pathway and Risk of Subsequent Recalls</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Kadakia%20KT"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Kushal T Kadakia</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
